OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy to start, soon
OL,6,Fclearing to give lengthy sunny spells.
OL,7,FVery warm or hot in the west, cooler
OL,8,Fin the east and near coasts especially
OL,9,Fin the strong winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear skies for most, except
OL,12,Fin the east and along the coast where
OL,13,Flow cloud will return and move inland,
OL,14,FWinds remain breezy and very gusty
OL,15,Falong the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FAny cloud will quickly burn
OL,18,Foff to give sunny spells. Very warm,
OL,19,Fperhaps hot inland, but cooler near
OL,20,Fcoasts, in very breezy winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
